GoFax,is,focused,on,provided,solutions,for,internet,fax,and,SMS,services,through,email,A,range,of,services,are,offered,from,Fax,and,SMS,integration,through,APIs,email,to,fax,sending,fax,to,email,receiving,and,email,to,SMS,sending,The,GoFax,SMS,service,allows,you,to,send,SMS,from,emails,a,third,party,application,or,their,desktop,service,You,can,send,automatic,SMS,reminders,as,well,as,confirmations,The,SOAP,based,SMS,API,allows,you,to,integrate,any,application,with,the,service,that,utilizes,HTTP,calls,Functions,include,creating,login,tokens,retrieving,SMS,details,sending,and,resending,SMS,messages,and,retrieval,of,recently,sent,messages,through,the,service